{"about_the_game":"Demons Happened is a fast paced action/puzzler with an enemy possession mechanic. Grab a demon, exploit its powers, fling it to the next one, and chain your kills in a perfect execution of your master plan... or miss a step, improvise, and quickly recover with a creative solution.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Handcrafted Levels</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992020/extras/gif_store_clock_compressed.gif?t=1661548883\" /><br>Try, fail, wing it, and try again until you bring your plan to perfection, all in the span of a few seconds. Set in a world where rent prices seem unaffected by humanity's demise, bite-size, handcrafted levels unfold in a series of challenges where every fight is a puzzle, and your enemies become the tools to overcome any obstacle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Use Your Enemies</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992020/extras/gif_store_bomb_compressed.gif?t=1661548883\" /><br>Possess everybody else's demons to confront and use a variety of powers. Shoot from a safe distance with passive-aggressiveness, explode with repressed anger, shield yourself with overprotectiveness, stop time with your stress, and pet some very cute rats spawned by cowardice, nice and fluffy.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992020/extras/gif_store_rat1.gif?t=1661548883\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Control your enemies to overcome your obstacles<br></li><li> 8 enemies with vastly different skills, from ricocheting bullets to time stopping<br></li><li> More than 100 bite-size levels, a mix of action, puzzle, and skillful dodging<br></li><li> Collectibles for an extra challenge<br></li><li> Two endings<br></li><li> A protagonist dead inside AND outside</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"All better now","path":"https://cdn.akama